<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_03_IH_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- <div id="app_wrap" class="ema511_01_ih_0001"> -->
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_03_ih_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3_orange" lang="y">직육면체의 부피는 몇 ㎤ 인지 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_03_IH/616_03_03_S.png" alt="" />
          <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_03_IH/616_03_03_L.png" alt="" />
        </div>

        <div class="box_cm">
          <span class="cm1">6 ㎝</span>
          <span class="cm2">5 ㎝</span>
          <span class="cm3">9 ㎝</span>
          <span class="cm4">10 ㎝</span>
          <span class="cm5">3 ㎝</span>
          <span class="cm6">8 ㎝</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify_center align_center">
          <div class="input_wrap">
            <math-field data-answer-single="270" text-align="center"></math-field>
          </div>
          <h2 class="mr_40"><span>㎤</span></h2>
          <div class="input_wrap second_answer ml_40">
            <math-field data-answer-single="240" text-align="center"></math-field>
          </div>
          <h2 class="second_answer"><span>㎤</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet">가로가 9 ㎝, 세로가 5 ㎝, 높이가 6 ㎝인 직육면체의 부피는 9×5×6=270 (㎤)입니다.</p>
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet">가로가 8 ㎝, 세로가 3 ㎝, 높이가 10 ㎝인 직육면체의 부피는 8×3×10=240 (㎤)입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve">
              <div>
                <button type="button" class="btnVideo"><span lang="y">해설 영상</span></button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
